1276499099.text: We recently reported that COX-2 and PGE2 induces Akt and GSK-3beta and wnt signaling (beta-catenin and T-cell factor and lymphoid enhancer factor) to increase MIG-7 that inhibits protein phosphatase 2A (PP2A) to positively feedback on Akt and GSK-3beta signaling and sustain cancer cell migration and invasion [XREF_BIBR].
